1
00:01:31,010 --> 00:01:34,920
[Dream of Golden Years]

2
00:01:35,229 --> 00:01:36,950
I didn't lose!

3
00:01:35,850 --> 00:01:39,300
[1998]

4
00:01:37,150 --> 00:01:38,590
Lele cheated.

5
00:01:38,710 --> 00:01:40,479
I didn't lose!

6
00:01:40,759 --> 00:01:41,350
Alright.

7
00:01:41,350 --> 00:01:42,350
It's just a game of soccer.

8
00:01:42,350 --> 00:01:43,120
Winning won't make you taller,

9
00:01:43,120 --> 00:01:44,789
and losing won't make you shrink, alright?

10
00:01:44,789 --> 00:01:45,840
Come on. Wash your hands and let's eat.

11
00:01:45,840 --> 00:01:46,310
Stop crying.

12
00:01:46,310 --> 00:01:47,840
I really didn't lose!

13
00:01:47,840 --> 00:01:48,310
Alright.

14
00:01:48,310 --> 00:01:49,310
I didn't lose.

15
00:01:49,310 --> 00:01:50,370
Alright, alright.

16
00:01:50,400 --> 00:01:52,920
Getting carried away with
that fake crying, huh?

17
00:01:52,920 --> 00:01:54,400
A real man should be able to
win with grace

18
00:01:54,400 --> 00:01:55,660
and lose with dignity.

19
00:01:55,710 --> 00:01:56,240
Besides,

20
00:01:56,280 --> 00:01:57,410
this isn't over yet.

21
00:01:57,680 --> 00:01:58,509
If you're not convinced,

22
00:01:58,509 --> 00:01:59,640
just win it back next time.

23
00:01:59,640 --> 00:02:00,170
Exactly.

24
00:02:00,200 --> 00:02:01,070
Everyone, come eat!

25
00:02:01,070 --> 00:02:02,270
Come on, let's go eat.

26
00:02:02,760 --> 00:02:03,790
That's life—

27
00:02:04,230 --> 00:02:05,230
until the very end,

28
00:02:05,230 --> 00:02:05,920
no one knows

29
00:02:05,920 --> 00:02:07,180
who the real winner is.

30
00:02:08,360 --> 00:02:09,120
He's just a kid.

31
00:02:09,120 --> 00:02:10,720
Why are you telling him this?

32
00:02:10,750 --> 00:02:11,210
Come on.

33
00:02:13,030 --> 00:02:13,630
Let's eat.

34
00:02:16,860 --> 00:02:20,200
[Episode 31]
[The Real Winner]

35
00:02:21,240 --> 00:02:22,630
The one who will receive 5% of

36
00:02:22,630 --> 00:02:24,090
Chengrong Group's shares

37
00:02:24,590 --> 00:02:25,079
is...

38
00:02:27,840 --> 00:02:28,590
Zhao...

39
00:02:33,240 --> 00:02:33,680
Hui.

40
00:02:37,240 --> 00:02:38,470
I knew I'd win!

41
00:02:40,120 --> 00:02:41,050
Come on! Come on!

42
00:02:41,520 --> 00:02:42,470
Go, Zhaohui!

43
00:02:45,630 --> 00:02:46,150
Come on!

44
00:02:46,800 --> 00:02:47,860
Come on! Well done!

45
00:02:48,360 --> 00:02:50,150
Go, Zhaohui! Go!

46
00:02:51,030 --> 00:02:51,560
Thanks.

47
00:02:51,750 --> 00:02:53,880
Congratulations. Congratulations.

48
00:02:56,610 --> 00:02:58,740
Thanks, everyone. Let's have a drink!

49
00:03:03,630 --> 00:03:04,150
Zhaoji,

50
00:03:04,800 --> 00:03:06,460
are you really okay with this?

51
00:03:07,030 --> 00:03:08,430
Daddy just favors Zhaohui more.

52
00:03:08,430 --> 00:03:09,890
What's not to be okay with?

53
00:03:09,910 --> 00:03:11,040
Congrats, Zhaohui.

54
00:03:11,840 --> 00:03:13,640
I don't get your brotherly love.

55
00:03:19,590 --> 00:03:19,910
Here.

56
00:03:19,700 --> 00:03:22,670
[Du Family Banquet]

57
00:03:27,910 --> 00:03:28,520
Remember,

58
00:03:28,590 --> 00:03:30,520
don't hurt that guy surnamed Zhou.

59
00:03:38,680 --> 00:03:40,410
-Quick, get in the car!
-Get in.

60
00:03:44,430 --> 00:03:44,960
Let's go.

61
00:04:02,710 --> 00:04:03,440
Stop the car!

62
00:04:17,510 --> 00:04:18,240
Stop the car!

63
00:04:22,950 --> 00:04:23,680
Stop the car!

64
00:04:26,800 --> 00:04:27,530
Stop the car!

65
00:04:32,150 --> 00:04:33,390
You dare hit me?

66
00:04:41,920 --> 00:04:42,560
Why wouldn't Old Man

67
00:04:42,560 --> 00:04:44,000
let us touch that guy surnamed Zhou?

68
00:04:44,000 --> 00:04:44,600
How would I know

69
00:04:44,600 --> 00:04:45,720
what Old Man is thinking?

70
00:04:45,720 --> 00:04:48,180
He just thinks so highly of
that Xia Xiaolan.

71
00:04:48,190 --> 00:04:48,720
But

72
00:04:49,190 --> 00:04:50,790
they took that Xiao guy away.

73
00:04:51,310 --> 00:04:52,909
Quan, you must be upset, too.

74
00:05:05,480 --> 00:05:06,070
Mr. Xiao.

75
00:05:06,800 --> 00:05:07,930
Do you still have it?

76
00:05:08,190 --> 00:05:08,600
Yes.

77
00:05:11,390 --> 00:05:12,750
I can't do anything right.

78
00:05:12,750 --> 00:05:14,150
They all say I'm an idiot.

79
00:05:15,000 --> 00:05:16,270
I bet they never thought I'd be the one

80
00:05:16,270 --> 00:05:17,400
to steal the ledger.

81
00:05:27,430 --> 00:05:28,090
Zhou Cheng.

82
00:05:29,360 --> 00:05:30,090
What is this?

83
00:05:32,110 --> 00:05:34,170
Liu Tianquan's smuggling accounts.

84
00:05:47,390 --> 00:05:47,920
Xiaolan.

85
00:05:48,480 --> 00:05:49,240
Are you okay?

86
00:05:49,600 --> 00:05:50,130
I'm fine.

87
00:05:50,720 --> 00:05:51,580
Okay, let's go.

88
00:05:51,720 --> 00:05:52,360
Ms. Xia.

89
00:05:53,830 --> 00:05:55,240
Chairman Du would like to
have a word with you.

90
00:05:55,240 --> 00:05:56,240
This way, please.

91
00:06:11,190 --> 00:06:11,920
Don't worry.

92
00:06:12,240 --> 00:06:13,920
San has left safely.

93
00:06:14,120 --> 00:06:15,070
It shows Chairman Du

94
00:06:15,070 --> 00:06:16,730
really didn't plan to harm us.

95
00:06:18,800 --> 00:06:20,330
I'll wait for you here then.

96
00:06:26,120 --> 00:06:27,650
Ms. Xia, please have a seat.

97
00:06:31,070 --> 00:06:32,240
Ms. Xia,

98
00:06:33,390 --> 00:06:35,190
are you satisfied with our hospitality

99
00:06:35,190 --> 00:06:35,870
today?

100
00:06:37,070 --> 00:06:38,550
You are too kind, Chairman Du.

101
00:06:38,550 --> 00:06:40,950
The banquet you prepared is
excellent, of course.

102
00:06:40,950 --> 00:06:42,070
It's just a pity

103
00:06:42,120 --> 00:06:43,190
that most guests

104
00:06:43,240 --> 00:06:44,640
didn't come for the food.

105
00:06:45,830 --> 00:06:47,070
Then are you satisfied with

106
00:06:47,070 --> 00:06:48,800
the outcome of the competition

107
00:06:49,680 --> 00:06:50,810
between my two sons?

108
00:06:52,390 --> 00:06:53,480
Whoever wins or loses

109
00:06:53,480 --> 00:06:55,280
is Chengrong Group's business.

110
00:06:55,600 --> 00:06:57,190
I'm Du Zhaohui's consultant.

111
00:06:57,190 --> 00:06:58,800
I'm certainly happy he won.

112
00:06:59,720 --> 00:07:00,560
But surely,

113
00:07:01,240 --> 00:07:02,360
Chairman Du, you wouldn't have

114
00:07:02,360 --> 00:07:03,830
declared Du Zhaohui the winner

115
00:07:03,830 --> 00:07:05,230
just to please me, right?

116
00:07:07,430 --> 00:07:08,160
Chairman Du,

117
00:07:08,360 --> 00:07:10,800
since you asked me here,
shouldn't we talk about

118
00:07:10,800 --> 00:07:12,310
the smuggling leads you mentioned

119
00:07:12,310 --> 00:07:13,600
in the invitation?

120
00:07:14,120 --> 00:07:15,120
Ms. Xia,

121
00:07:15,120 --> 00:07:16,980
you really are straightforward.

122
00:07:17,040 --> 00:07:19,300
Then I won't beat around the bush either.

123
00:07:19,750 --> 00:07:20,880
I've made up my mind—

124
00:07:21,270 --> 00:07:22,750
I'll shut down all of Chengrong Group's

125
00:07:22,750 --> 00:07:24,600
smuggling activities.

126
00:07:25,070 --> 00:07:27,070
If I find anyone

127
00:07:27,070 --> 00:07:29,000
still involved in smuggling,

128
00:07:29,040 --> 00:07:30,830
I'll hand them over

129
00:07:31,070 --> 00:07:33,270
to the Shengcheng Police immediately.

130
00:07:33,680 --> 00:07:34,360
That way,

131
00:07:35,070 --> 00:07:37,360
Mayor Tang should be pleased, right?

132
00:07:38,260 --> 00:07:39,890
I think your decision

133
00:07:39,920 --> 00:07:41,120
is absolutely right.

134
00:07:41,680 --> 00:07:42,510
But I must

135
00:07:42,510 --> 00:07:43,510
remind you—

136
00:07:43,920 --> 00:07:45,590
this is only the minimum requirement

137
00:07:45,590 --> 00:07:46,830
for Chengrong Group to do business
in Shengcheng,

138
00:07:46,830 --> 00:07:48,430
not a gesture of goodwill.

139
00:07:48,920 --> 00:07:50,070
What Shengcheng needs

140
00:07:50,070 --> 00:07:51,390
isn't any particular group

141
00:07:51,390 --> 00:07:52,159
or capital,

142
00:07:52,800 --> 00:07:54,190
but a law-abiding enterprise

143
00:07:54,190 --> 00:07:55,390
that can

144
00:07:55,750 --> 00:07:57,720
contribute to economic growth.

145
00:08:01,330 --> 00:08:02,090
Ms. Xia,

146
00:08:02,120 --> 00:08:03,510
you really are a woman of principle.

147
00:08:03,510 --> 00:08:04,680
No wonder Zhaohui

148
00:08:05,120 --> 00:08:06,630
didn't catch your eye.

149
00:08:07,800 --> 00:08:09,400
You flatter me, Chairman Du.

150
00:08:09,430 --> 00:08:10,510
Du Zhaohui is

151
00:08:10,510 --> 00:08:12,170
a very good business partner,

152
00:08:12,560 --> 00:08:13,720
but feelings

153
00:08:13,950 --> 00:08:15,750
and business are two entirely
different matters,

154
00:08:15,750 --> 00:08:16,480
aren't they?

155
00:08:17,070 --> 00:08:17,800
Otherwise,

156
00:08:18,160 --> 00:08:19,040
Chairman Du,

157
00:08:19,240 --> 00:08:21,100
if you really wanted to please me,

158
00:08:21,240 --> 00:08:22,630
wouldn't it be simpler

159
00:08:22,920 --> 00:08:24,580
to hand over the other person?

160
00:08:30,310 --> 00:08:31,120
Ms. Xia.

161
00:08:33,260 --> 00:08:34,440
Actually, by coming to Kong Island,

162
00:08:34,440 --> 00:08:35,789
you and Mr. Zhou have already gotten

163
00:08:35,789 --> 00:08:37,200
what you wanted.

164
00:08:38,440 --> 00:08:39,720
And I haven't laid a finger

165
00:08:39,720 --> 00:08:41,150
on Mr. Zhou.

166
00:08:43,200 --> 00:08:45,330
One shouldn't be too greedy, you know?

167
00:08:48,750 --> 00:08:49,670
In that case,

168
00:08:50,270 --> 00:08:52,530
I understand what you mean, Chairman Du.

169
00:08:52,720 --> 00:08:54,780
I hope you'll also keep your promise.

170
00:08:55,200 --> 00:08:56,530
I'll take my leave then.

171
00:08:56,550 --> 00:08:58,150
Do you really not want to know

172
00:08:58,170 --> 00:08:59,720
why I chose Zhaohui

173
00:08:59,720 --> 00:09:01,120
instead of Zhaoji?

174
00:09:02,720 --> 00:09:03,480
Du Zhaoji

175
00:09:03,510 --> 00:09:05,670
is too much like you
when you first made your fortune—

176
00:09:05,670 --> 00:09:06,360
ambitious

177
00:09:06,550 --> 00:09:07,680
and without limits.

178
00:09:07,790 --> 00:09:08,550
And you know

179
00:09:08,870 --> 00:09:10,080
that kind of approach doesn't work anymore

180
00:09:10,080 --> 00:09:11,150
in this day and age.

181
00:09:11,960 --> 00:09:13,690
Kong Island is returning soon.

182
00:09:15,790 --> 00:09:17,150
Impressive.

183
00:09:17,840 --> 00:09:18,360
You know,

184
00:09:18,360 --> 00:09:19,290
sometimes I feel

185
00:09:20,550 --> 00:09:21,440
you're nothing like

186
00:09:21,440 --> 00:09:22,750
a twenty-year-old.

187
00:09:23,200 --> 00:09:24,200
Thanks for the compliment.

188
00:09:24,200 --> 00:09:25,530
I'll take my leave then.

189
00:09:41,600 --> 00:09:42,960
That Xia Xiaolan

190
00:09:43,150 --> 00:09:44,240
is so rude.

191
00:09:44,360 --> 00:09:46,160
Just because she's the mayor's daughter,

192
00:09:46,160 --> 00:09:48,820
she thinks she can talk to you like that,
Master?

193
00:09:50,870 --> 00:09:51,790
I don't think

194
00:09:52,030 --> 00:09:53,510
you need to be so sarcastic

195
00:09:53,510 --> 00:09:55,080
over a little grudge

196
00:09:55,080 --> 00:09:56,960
with your cousin.

197
00:09:59,380 --> 00:09:59,900
I...

198
00:10:00,360 --> 00:10:01,150
Look,

199
00:10:01,790 --> 00:10:03,390
since you already have a new identity,

200
00:10:03,390 --> 00:10:05,120
just play your role properly.

201
00:10:08,110 --> 00:10:08,750
Master.

202
00:10:09,750 --> 00:10:10,810
You knew all along?

203
00:10:16,150 --> 00:10:16,750
It's fine.

204
00:10:17,870 --> 00:10:18,630
You know,

205
00:10:19,030 --> 00:10:21,600
anyone who gets close to me—

206
00:10:22,030 --> 00:10:24,160
I make sure to know them inside and out.

207
00:10:25,120 --> 00:10:26,870
Actually, I don't care

208
00:10:26,870 --> 00:10:28,200
about your background.

209
00:10:29,790 --> 00:10:31,150
What matters is

210
00:10:31,720 --> 00:10:33,030
that you serve me well.

211
00:10:34,080 --> 00:10:35,630
Whether you are Xia Ziyu

212
00:10:35,960 --> 00:10:37,000
or Vivi

213
00:10:37,200 --> 00:10:39,030
doesn't matter.

214
00:10:40,160 --> 00:10:41,470
What matters is

215
00:10:43,870 --> 00:10:44,730
that you are now

216
00:10:45,390 --> 00:10:47,240
the mother of my child.

217
00:10:50,390 --> 00:10:51,870
This is an indisputable fact.

218
00:10:51,870 --> 00:10:53,670
No one would dare to question it.

219
00:10:56,840 --> 00:10:58,550
Then can I go anywhere?

220
00:11:00,080 --> 00:11:01,550
Can I go to Shengcheng?

221
00:11:03,000 --> 00:11:03,960
Of course.

222
00:11:13,210 --> 00:11:14,670
According to Du Chengrong,

223
00:11:14,670 --> 00:11:16,530
he gave up that ledger on purpose.

224
00:11:17,510 --> 00:11:18,750
I've checked the ledger.

225
00:11:18,750 --> 00:11:20,240
The signature belongs to Liu Tianquan.

226
00:11:20,240 --> 00:11:21,150
It won't be long

227
00:11:21,150 --> 00:11:23,000
before Liu Tianquan is arrested.

228
00:11:23,000 --> 00:11:24,510
Giving up just Liu Tianquan

229
00:11:24,510 --> 00:11:26,320
to secure Shengcheng's resources—

230
00:11:26,320 --> 00:11:28,240
Du Chengrong is being far too optimistic.

231
00:11:28,240 --> 00:11:29,910
I don't believe he'd really give up

232
00:11:29,910 --> 00:11:31,480
all that off-the-books income.

233
00:11:31,480 --> 00:11:32,270
In the short term,

234
00:11:32,270 --> 00:11:33,750
Du Zhaohui will be Chengrong Group's

235
00:11:33,750 --> 00:11:35,550
representative in Shengcheng.

236
00:11:36,120 --> 00:11:36,790
If Du Zhaohui

237
00:11:36,790 --> 00:11:38,450
can stick to the current path,

238
00:11:38,790 --> 00:11:39,630
then at least Chengrong

239
00:11:39,630 --> 00:11:41,490
won't be left behind by the times.

240
00:11:43,840 --> 00:11:44,640
Young Master.

241
00:11:44,790 --> 00:11:45,480
Aren't you going back

242
00:11:45,480 --> 00:11:46,880
to Shengcheng with them?

243
00:11:48,560 --> 00:11:49,550
Our cooperation was only for the purpose

244
00:11:49,550 --> 00:11:51,150
of winning this competition.

245
00:11:51,150 --> 00:11:52,360
Now that the competition is won,

246
00:11:52,360 --> 00:11:53,760
the cooperation is over.

247
00:11:54,510 --> 00:11:55,630
What reason do I have

248
00:11:55,630 --> 00:11:56,790
to stay by her side?

249
00:11:58,330 --> 00:11:59,330
As for Du Zhaoji,

250
00:11:59,360 --> 00:12:01,290
he won't accept defeat willingly.

251
00:12:01,480 --> 00:12:04,210
I have to stay in Kong Island
to guard against him.

252
00:12:09,360 --> 00:12:10,360
When you go back,

253
00:12:11,240 --> 00:12:12,840
settle her consulting fees.

254
00:12:12,960 --> 00:12:13,320
Okay.

255
00:12:13,870 --> 00:12:15,000
Now that she's gone,

256
00:12:15,620 --> 00:12:17,420
who knows when we'll meet again.

257
00:12:20,170 --> 00:12:21,320
Young Master, you... You...

258
00:12:21,320 --> 00:12:23,080
Are you lovesick again?

259
00:12:41,360 --> 00:12:42,480
You old fool...

260
00:12:42,870 --> 00:12:43,840
You old fool!

261
00:12:48,660 --> 00:12:49,750
All my efforts to be a dutiful son

262
00:12:49,750 --> 00:12:50,750
were for nothing!

263
00:12:51,480 --> 00:12:52,960
In the end, you still gave

264
00:12:54,200 --> 00:12:55,670
to Du Zhaohui.

265
00:12:57,600 --> 00:13:00,930
You've really become more and more
muddle-headed with age.

266
00:13:21,790 --> 00:13:24,320
I'll take back everything
that belongs to me.

267
00:14:01,200 --> 00:14:02,330
Go report to Ms. Xia—

268
00:14:02,670 --> 00:14:04,480
the Golden Sands Pool
model room is finished.

269
00:14:04,480 --> 00:14:04,910
Got it.

270
00:14:08,710 --> 00:14:11,110
[Kong Island]

271
00:14:11,580 --> 00:14:15,540
[Chengrong Group]

272
00:14:25,560 --> 00:14:26,090
Hua,

273
00:14:26,390 --> 00:14:27,240
make an appointment with Dr. Liu

274
00:14:27,240 --> 00:14:28,240
for a heart check-up.

275
00:14:28,240 --> 00:14:29,440
Where... Where does your heart hurt?

276
00:14:29,440 --> 00:14:30,510
I'll go get the doctor right away.

277
00:14:30,510 --> 00:14:32,370
Every time I think of Xia Xiaolan,

278
00:14:32,600 --> 00:14:33,600
my heart aches.

279
00:14:33,780 --> 00:14:39,440
♪ Love has faded,
and so has the bond between us ♪

280
00:14:34,510 --> 00:14:35,270
Since the birthday banquet,

281
00:14:35,270 --> 00:14:36,910
I haven't seen her for 2 months.

282
00:14:36,910 --> 00:14:38,110
Two months, you know?

283
00:14:39,150 --> 00:14:40,360
I'm afraid I've got lovesickness.

284
00:14:39,760 --> 00:14:48,650
♪ Yet, why do I still love you? ♪

285
00:14:40,510 --> 00:14:41,790
Lovesickness?

286
00:14:42,080 --> 00:14:43,480
You need to see a psychiatrist
for lovesickness,

287
00:14:43,480 --> 00:14:44,280
Young Master.

288
00:14:46,840 --> 00:14:48,080
You know,

289
00:14:48,790 --> 00:14:49,850
I see them often...

290
00:14:50,750 --> 00:14:52,120
Our premium buildings
even come with a household registration,

291
00:14:52,120 --> 00:14:53,390
so there's no reason for them to be cheap.

292
00:14:53,390 --> 00:14:54,870
The first floor can be priced a bit higher

293
00:14:54,870 --> 00:14:56,520
since it comes with
an underground parking space.

294
00:14:56,520 --> 00:14:57,960
The second and third floors
are good levels—

295
00:14:57,960 --> 00:14:59,030
easy to walk up to

296
00:14:59,030 --> 00:15:00,200
and not damp to live in.

297
00:15:00,200 --> 00:15:01,550
The fourth and fifth floors
have great views,

298
00:15:01,550 --> 00:15:03,910
so their prices definitely
shouldn't be lowered.

299
00:15:03,910 --> 00:15:05,390
And the top floor comes with a garden,

300
00:15:05,390 --> 00:15:07,000
so pricing it a bit higher is no problem.

301
00:15:07,000 --> 00:15:07,330
Okay.

302
00:15:07,670 --> 00:15:08,470
Ms. Xia, look—

303
00:15:08,670 --> 00:15:10,530
the newly installed scale model.

304
00:15:10,630 --> 00:15:11,550
See if there's anything

305
00:15:11,550 --> 00:15:12,880
that needs adjustment.

306
00:15:19,480 --> 00:15:20,080
Gong Yang.

307
00:15:21,080 --> 00:15:22,540
You made this scale model?

308
00:15:24,360 --> 00:15:25,480
So is there anything

309
00:15:25,480 --> 00:15:27,140
that needs correcting to you?

310
00:15:27,270 --> 00:15:28,480
I don't think there is.

311
00:15:28,480 --> 00:15:29,610
I'll check it again.

312
00:15:30,200 --> 00:15:30,630
Okay.

313
00:15:35,800 --> 00:15:37,260
Send the drawings in a bit.

314
00:15:37,510 --> 00:15:38,390
This Building 9—

315
00:15:38,390 --> 00:15:39,790
let's make it the special offer building.

316
00:15:39,790 --> 00:15:40,120
Okay.

317
00:15:40,150 --> 00:15:41,840
The lighting probably isn't very good.

318
00:15:41,840 --> 00:15:42,770
Let's sell it for

319
00:15:43,240 --> 00:15:44,200
2,000 yuan per square meter.

320
00:15:44,200 --> 00:15:44,910
2,000...

321
00:15:45,030 --> 00:15:46,960
2,000 yuan per square meter
is the special offer?

322
00:15:46,960 --> 00:15:47,470
Yes.

323
00:15:47,830 --> 00:15:49,240
Compared to the list price,

324
00:15:49,240 --> 00:15:50,770
it's already much cheaper.

325
00:15:51,360 --> 00:15:52,270
Write this down.

326
00:15:52,270 --> 00:15:53,600
This is the viewing process

327
00:15:53,600 --> 00:15:54,660
for the launch day:

328
00:15:54,720 --> 00:15:56,650
first, we show the customers
the scale model.

329
00:15:56,650 --> 00:15:57,890
Once they've decided on a unit type,

330
00:15:57,890 --> 00:15:58,940
they pay a 1,000-yuan

331
00:15:58,940 --> 00:15:59,840
reservation deposit,

332
00:15:59,840 --> 00:16:00,630
and then we can take them

333
00:16:00,630 --> 00:16:01,870
into the residential complex.

334
00:16:01,870 --> 00:16:02,330
Ms. Xia.

335
00:16:02,480 --> 00:16:05,270
You mean they have to pay before viewing,

336
00:16:05,270 --> 00:16:05,750
right?

337
00:16:06,480 --> 00:16:06,840
Yes.

338
00:16:07,150 --> 00:16:08,080
That 1,000 yuan

339
00:16:08,130 --> 00:16:09,200
will be counted towards the house price.

340
00:16:09,200 --> 00:16:10,240
We won't just take it.

341
00:16:10,240 --> 00:16:11,080
If they aren't willing

342
00:16:11,080 --> 00:16:12,240
to pay even this 1,000 yuan,

343
00:16:12,240 --> 00:16:13,360
how can we expect them to fork out

344
00:16:13,360 --> 00:16:14,150
more money?

345
00:16:15,200 --> 00:16:17,130
This is called precise screening.

346
00:16:17,150 --> 00:16:18,010
Serious buyers

347
00:16:18,080 --> 00:16:19,680
will save us a lot of trouble.

348
00:16:20,240 --> 00:16:21,370
Brilliant, Ms. Xia.

349
00:16:21,630 --> 00:16:23,550
If there are no questions,

350
00:16:23,550 --> 00:16:24,840
compile the information

351
00:16:24,840 --> 00:16:25,650
I just gave you,

352
00:16:25,650 --> 00:16:27,000
and send it to the newspaper
for publication.

353
00:16:27,000 --> 00:16:27,330
Okay.

354
00:16:27,390 --> 00:16:28,870
There are 2 months until the launch.

355
00:16:28,870 --> 00:16:29,950
We can't stop advertising.

356
00:16:29,950 --> 00:16:30,790
The closer we get,

357
00:16:30,790 --> 00:16:31,720
the more effort we need to put in.

358
00:16:31,720 --> 00:16:32,050
Okay.

359
00:16:34,320 --> 00:16:34,840
Ms. Xia,

360
00:16:35,150 --> 00:16:36,360
the model room is ready.

361
00:16:36,360 --> 00:16:37,390
Shall we go over now?

362
00:16:37,390 --> 00:16:37,750
Okay.

363
00:16:39,790 --> 00:16:40,390
Gong Yang.

364
00:16:42,150 --> 00:16:43,750
The scale model is well made.

365
00:16:43,840 --> 00:16:45,030
There are still many tasks
for you to handle

366
00:16:45,030 --> 00:16:46,090
before the launch.

367
00:16:46,120 --> 00:16:47,180
Keep up the effort.

368
00:16:47,320 --> 00:16:47,790
Ms. Xia,

369
00:16:48,360 --> 00:16:49,240
I'll do my best.

370
00:16:51,750 --> 00:16:53,610
No one understands better than me

371
00:16:53,670 --> 00:16:54,870
how precious

372
00:16:54,870 --> 00:16:55,930
a second chance is.

373
00:16:57,000 --> 00:16:57,960
If I can give someone

374
00:16:57,960 --> 00:16:58,720
this chance,

375
00:16:59,120 --> 00:17:00,240
I don't want to be stingy.

376
00:17:00,240 --> 00:17:00,770
Let's go.

377
00:17:01,000 --> 00:17:01,360
Okay.

378
00:17:07,030 --> 00:17:07,750
Paying 50,000 yuan a year

379
00:17:07,750 --> 00:17:09,550
for a regular membership

380
00:17:09,790 --> 00:17:11,750
versus 100,000 yuan for a VIP membership

381
00:17:11,750 --> 00:17:12,589
for golf—

382
00:17:12,589 --> 00:17:14,390
what exactly is the difference?

383
00:17:14,520 --> 00:17:16,170
Regular members and us VIPs

384
00:17:16,200 --> 00:17:17,530
are not in the same zone.

385
00:17:17,579 --> 00:17:19,000
There's also premium membership,

386
00:17:19,000 --> 00:17:20,069
which is by invitation only.

387
00:17:20,069 --> 00:17:21,640
It's not something you can just buy.

388
00:17:21,640 --> 00:17:22,720
It's that hard?

389
00:17:23,859 --> 00:17:25,560
I think Auntie is right.

390
00:17:25,720 --> 00:17:26,829
Instead of spending time here,

391
00:17:26,829 --> 00:17:27,589
we'd be better off working in the shop.

392
00:17:27,589 --> 00:17:29,510
We could close several big deals
in one morning.

393
00:17:29,510 --> 00:17:30,440
Exactly.

394
00:17:31,030 --> 00:17:32,150
Zhenzhu, Auntie.

395
00:17:32,270 --> 00:17:32,790
Coming here

396
00:17:32,790 --> 00:17:34,540
isn't about playing golf.

397
00:17:34,680 --> 00:17:35,590
It's for the

398
00:17:35,590 --> 00:17:37,650
exclusive social environment here.

399
00:17:37,830 --> 00:17:38,880
People prefer to associate

400
00:17:38,880 --> 00:17:40,240
with those on their own level.

401
00:17:40,240 --> 00:17:42,240
It's called exchanging resources.

402
00:17:43,160 --> 00:17:43,830
Mr. Chen.

403
00:17:45,360 --> 00:17:46,370
Hello, hello.

404
00:17:46,400 --> 00:17:46,750
Look.

405
00:17:46,790 --> 00:17:48,070
I don't have your contact info yet.

406
00:17:48,070 --> 00:17:48,330
So...

407
00:17:48,330 --> 00:17:49,390
I have it, I have it.

408
00:17:49,680 --> 00:17:50,110
Here.

409
00:17:52,070 --> 00:17:53,350
Chen Xiliang from Luna.

410
00:17:53,350 --> 00:17:53,960
Here's my card.

411
00:17:53,960 --> 00:17:54,490
Alright.

412
00:17:54,680 --> 00:17:55,280
Thank you.

413
00:17:55,310 --> 00:17:56,240
Let's keep in touch.

414
00:17:56,240 --> 00:17:56,830
Sure.

415
00:17:56,830 --> 00:17:57,760
Nice to meet you.

416
00:17:59,200 --> 00:18:01,440
Doing business is that simple?

417
00:18:02,000 --> 00:18:03,880
Starting from scratch is hard, of course.

418
00:18:03,880 --> 00:18:05,550
But once you have a solid foundation,

419
00:18:05,550 --> 00:18:07,350
stepping onto the right platform

420
00:18:07,350 --> 00:18:09,240
just opens up all kinds of opportunities.

421
00:18:09,240 --> 00:18:11,400
Then we should have asked your mom
to come along today.

422
00:18:11,400 --> 00:18:12,590
She's now Luna's

423
00:18:12,920 --> 00:18:14,200
regional manager.

424
00:18:14,550 --> 00:18:16,280
She needs a platform like this.

425
00:18:16,400 --> 00:18:16,920
But my mom

426
00:18:16,920 --> 00:18:18,200
is not only a regional manager now—

427
00:18:18,200 --> 00:18:19,700
she's also the mayor's wife.

428
00:18:19,700 --> 00:18:20,550
This kind of environment

429
00:18:20,550 --> 00:18:21,550
doesn't suit her.

430
00:18:21,810 --> 00:18:22,200
I forgot.

431
00:18:22,200 --> 00:18:23,680
O-Our Teresa is the same.

432
00:18:23,790 --> 00:18:25,510
She can't come unless she's paid.

433
00:18:25,510 --> 00:18:26,240
Right, right.

434
00:18:26,240 --> 00:18:27,240
-She's a superstar, after all.
-Chen.

435
00:18:27,240 --> 00:18:28,220
You're talking nonsense.

436
00:18:28,220 --> 00:18:29,950
That's completely different.

437
00:18:29,960 --> 00:18:30,790
And once we do,

438
00:18:30,790 --> 00:18:33,030
we're gonna have parks for children,

439
00:18:33,030 --> 00:18:34,690
entertainment areas, and...

440
00:18:34,750 --> 00:18:36,510
Isn't that Ms. Xia?

441
00:18:37,110 --> 00:18:38,240
What a coincidence.

442
00:18:40,440 --> 00:18:40,970
Zhaohui!

443
00:18:42,830 --> 00:18:43,360
Xiaolan!

444
00:18:44,440 --> 00:18:47,420
[Shengcheng: A City of Innovation
and Charm—Welcome!]

445
00:19:11,880 --> 00:19:13,610
Mr. Du is honored to be invited,

446
00:19:13,750 --> 00:19:15,210
but he's abroad right now.

447
00:19:15,960 --> 00:19:17,090
So I'll be attending

448
00:19:17,350 --> 00:19:18,200
on his behalf.

449
00:19:20,700 --> 00:19:21,880
Ladies and gentlemen,

450
00:19:21,880 --> 00:19:22,810
hello everyone.

451
00:19:23,070 --> 00:19:24,720
We gather here today

452
00:19:25,100 --> 00:19:26,960
to witness the opening of
the Oriental Green

453
00:19:26,960 --> 00:19:28,510
Golf Club.

454
00:19:28,690 --> 00:19:30,320
I hope this green course

455
00:19:30,350 --> 00:19:31,830
can bring joy to everyone.

456
00:19:31,850 --> 00:19:34,180
She dares to come to Shengcheng so openly—

457
00:19:34,350 --> 00:19:35,480
it seems Chairman Du

458
00:19:35,550 --> 00:19:38,150
has already taken care of
her identity issues.

459
00:19:38,880 --> 00:19:40,400
Why did Old Man send her?

460
00:19:40,830 --> 00:19:42,750
It makes sense that Chairman Du
doesn't show up,

461
00:19:42,750 --> 00:19:43,900
but shouldn't he have

462
00:19:43,900 --> 00:19:44,960
let you, Young Master Du,

463
00:19:44,960 --> 00:19:46,160
attend on his behalf?

464
00:19:46,790 --> 00:19:48,250
Why let her do the tee-off?

465
00:19:49,310 --> 00:19:49,960
Xia Ziyu

466
00:19:50,030 --> 00:19:51,890
is pregnant with Old Man's child.

467
00:19:52,110 --> 00:19:53,590
She took the chance to tell him

468
00:19:53,590 --> 00:19:55,920
that she wants to learn
how to do business.

469
00:19:56,320 --> 00:19:57,440
For such public appearances,

470
00:19:57,440 --> 00:19:59,030
she's always the first to volunteer.

471
00:19:59,030 --> 00:20:01,110
Then I must congratulate you,
Young Master Du,

472
00:20:01,110 --> 00:20:03,240
on getting another brother or sister.

473
00:20:03,350 --> 00:20:04,510
Don't tease me.

474
00:20:05,390 --> 00:20:06,790
Old Man lets her have the spotlight

475
00:20:06,790 --> 00:20:08,120
just to keep me in check—

476
00:20:08,200 --> 00:20:09,040
to let me know

477
00:20:09,310 --> 00:20:10,400
that even though I won the shares,

478
00:20:10,400 --> 00:20:11,730
I shouldn't be too smug.

479
00:20:12,390 --> 00:20:13,310
He won't really give his fortune

480
00:20:13,310 --> 00:20:14,350
to her.

481
00:20:15,030 --> 00:20:15,640
But you—

482
00:20:15,790 --> 00:20:17,000
her hatred for you is real.

483
00:20:17,000 --> 00:20:18,400
You'd better be careful.

484
00:20:20,550 --> 00:20:21,790
Xia Ziyu?

485
00:20:22,200 --> 00:20:23,480
You mean that Xia Ziyu?

486
00:20:24,720 --> 00:20:25,680
Where is she?

487
00:20:26,640 --> 00:20:27,300
Over there.

488
00:20:29,790 --> 00:20:31,160
Isn't she a fugitive?

489
00:20:31,480 --> 00:20:32,940
We should call the police.

490
00:20:33,200 --> 00:20:34,480
She's got a new identity.

491
00:20:34,480 --> 00:20:35,250
Even if we report her to the police,

492
00:20:35,250 --> 00:20:36,680
they won't be able to catch her
anytime soon.

493
00:20:36,680 --> 00:20:37,550
Dear friends...

494
00:20:37,550 --> 00:20:38,030
My goodness.

495
00:20:38,030 --> 00:20:39,720
Why does she look like that?

496
00:20:40,070 --> 00:20:40,590
Ready?

497
00:20:41,200 --> 00:20:41,640
Three.

498
00:20:42,960 --> 00:20:43,550
Two.

499
00:20:44,480 --> 00:20:44,960
One.

500
00:20:45,510 --> 00:20:46,240
Tee off!

501
00:20:49,720 --> 00:20:51,960
-Great!
-Nice!

502
00:20:53,640 --> 00:20:55,360
Thank you all, distinguished guests.

503
00:20:55,360 --> 00:20:56,480
Now, Oriental Green

504
00:20:56,480 --> 00:20:57,400
Golf Club

505
00:20:57,420 --> 00:20:58,900
is officially open!

506
00:21:01,440 --> 00:21:02,600
So that's Xia Ziyu?

507
00:21:02,920 --> 00:21:03,480
Yeah.

508
00:21:03,960 --> 00:21:06,160
The notorious Xia Ziyu.

509
00:21:07,400 --> 00:21:08,440
Shall we go out for a drink?

510
00:21:08,440 --> 00:21:08,970
Zhaohui!

511
00:21:10,750 --> 00:21:11,480
If I'd known you wanted to come,

512
00:21:11,480 --> 00:21:13,010
you could have come with me.

513
00:21:13,030 --> 00:21:15,290
Why are you stuck in the regular section?

514
00:21:15,880 --> 00:21:17,160
Do you guys

515
00:21:17,160 --> 00:21:17,920
smell that?

516
00:21:18,350 --> 00:21:19,920
That musky, foul stench—

517
00:21:20,440 --> 00:21:21,400
you know, like a wild fox

518
00:21:21,400 --> 00:21:21,920
that's been caged for ages

519
00:21:21,920 --> 00:21:23,110
just got released.

520
00:21:23,550 --> 00:21:24,550
Unbearably foul.

521
00:21:24,680 --> 00:21:25,200
Xiaolan,

522
00:21:25,200 --> 00:21:25,700
let's go.

523
00:21:25,700 --> 00:21:26,160
Let's get some fresh air.

524
00:21:26,160 --> 00:21:27,890
Why leave as soon as I come over?

525
00:21:28,240 --> 00:21:30,640
Don't think of yourself as insignificant.

526
00:21:31,510 --> 00:21:33,400
Come to think of it, isn't all this wealth

527
00:21:33,400 --> 00:21:34,680
I have thanks to you?

528
00:21:36,200 --> 00:21:38,330
The person I should be most grateful to

529
00:21:38,880 --> 00:21:39,650
is you.

530
00:21:45,960 --> 00:21:48,270
Seems like you two
have business to settle.

531
00:21:48,270 --> 00:21:49,670
I'll excuse myself then.

532
00:21:52,270 --> 00:21:52,830
Goodbye,

533
00:21:53,720 --> 00:21:54,450
Xia Xiaolan.

534
00:22:02,910 --> 00:22:03,920
Disgusting.

535
00:22:04,640 --> 00:22:05,300
Du Zhaohui.

536
00:22:07,070 --> 00:22:07,830
Is there something

537
00:22:07,830 --> 00:22:08,890
you want to tell me?

538
00:22:22,070 --> 00:22:23,870
I kept asking you out for coffee,

539
00:22:24,070 --> 00:22:25,400
but you never accepted.

540
00:22:25,960 --> 00:22:26,510
Now look—

541
00:22:27,440 --> 00:22:29,240
we're finally having coffee together.

542
00:22:29,240 --> 00:22:29,790
But this is probably

543
00:22:29,790 --> 00:22:30,990
the last cup, I guess.

544
00:22:32,400 --> 00:22:33,110
You know,

545
00:22:33,510 --> 00:22:34,270
back then,

546
00:22:34,480 --> 00:22:35,880
we weren't partners yet.

547
00:22:36,840 --> 00:22:38,110
I wanted to use a honey trap

548
00:22:38,110 --> 00:22:38,960
on Old Man.

549
00:22:39,750 --> 00:22:41,070
I noticed that Xia Ziyu

550
00:22:41,400 --> 00:22:42,510
was quite thick-skinned,

551
00:22:42,510 --> 00:22:43,610
and she was a fugitive.

552
00:22:43,610 --> 00:22:44,770
She was like a pawn delivered to my door.

553
00:22:44,770 --> 00:22:46,230
I'd be a fool not to use her.

554
00:22:48,350 --> 00:22:50,150
I didn't mean to hide it from you.

555
00:22:50,160 --> 00:22:50,920
I just couldn't find

556
00:22:50,920 --> 00:22:52,380
the right time to tell you.

557
00:22:53,510 --> 00:22:53,920
When I found out

558
00:22:53,920 --> 00:22:55,380
about your relationship,

559
00:22:56,200 --> 00:22:57,660
I thought this connection

560
00:22:58,160 --> 00:22:58,640
might be useful

561
00:22:58,640 --> 00:22:59,720
in the future,

562
00:23:00,400 --> 00:23:01,800
so I didn't say anything.

563
00:23:02,380 --> 00:23:03,040
But later,

564
00:23:03,070 --> 00:23:05,270
we started working together, you know.

565
00:23:05,590 --> 00:23:06,590
I was worried that

566
00:23:06,790 --> 00:23:07,920
once you found out,

567
00:23:08,310 --> 00:23:10,350
we wouldn't be able to
continue our partnership,

568
00:23:10,350 --> 00:23:11,960
so I didn't dare to say anything.

569
00:23:11,960 --> 00:23:14,640
There are actually things
you don't dare to do, Young Master Du?

570
00:23:14,640 --> 00:23:15,900
Harboring a fugitive,

571
00:23:16,230 --> 00:23:17,480
getting her plastic surgery,

572
00:23:17,480 --> 00:23:18,740
teaching her to dance,

573
00:23:18,830 --> 00:23:19,680
and even sending her

574
00:23:19,680 --> 00:23:21,140
to your own father's side—

575
00:23:21,750 --> 00:23:22,680
Young Master Du,

576
00:23:22,830 --> 00:23:24,760
I think you've got plenty of nerve.

577
00:23:26,640 --> 00:23:27,590
Let me guess.

578
00:23:28,550 --> 00:23:30,480
Don't tell me you also wanted to see

579
00:23:30,490 --> 00:23:31,480
if Xia Ziyu has the ability

580
00:23:31,480 --> 00:23:33,140
to seduce both father and son?

581
00:23:33,200 --> 00:23:34,110
If even Du Zhaoji

582
00:23:34,110 --> 00:23:35,200
takes her bait,

583
00:23:35,560 --> 00:23:37,800
then you could just sit back and watch

584
00:23:37,830 --> 00:23:39,830
the father and son
turn against each other, right?

585
00:23:39,830 --> 00:23:41,480
Don't... Don't put it like that.

586
00:23:41,480 --> 00:23:41,830
I...

587
00:23:43,240 --> 00:23:44,240
At the time, I couldn't figure out

588
00:23:44,240 --> 00:23:45,840
what my old man was thinking,

589
00:23:46,440 --> 00:23:47,350
and I wasn't willing to let

590
00:23:47,350 --> 00:23:49,810
the Du family be snatched away
by that loser.

591
00:23:51,960 --> 00:23:52,820
I've never been

592
00:23:53,030 --> 00:23:54,560
afraid of anyone in my life,

593
00:23:55,240 --> 00:23:56,440
but honestly...

594
00:23:57,880 --> 00:23:58,400
I really feared

595
00:23:58,400 --> 00:23:59,110
you'd never speak to me again

596
00:23:59,110 --> 00:24:00,040
because of this.

597
00:24:02,070 --> 00:24:03,030
I knew that

598
00:24:05,030 --> 00:24:06,480
we could never date.

599
00:24:07,160 --> 00:24:08,000
But if we could

600
00:24:08,030 --> 00:24:09,630
continue working together,

601
00:24:09,720 --> 00:24:10,980
that would be nice too.

602
00:24:12,510 --> 00:24:13,400
But it seems

603
00:24:14,400 --> 00:24:16,000
that's also impossible now.

604
00:24:17,880 --> 00:24:19,080
I have no one to blame.

605
00:24:19,830 --> 00:24:20,790
I can only blame myself

606
00:24:20,790 --> 00:24:22,190
for meeting you too late.

607
00:24:26,400 --> 00:24:27,030
Mr. Du.

608
00:24:28,550 --> 00:24:31,080
If there are suitable projects
in the future,

609
00:24:31,480 --> 00:24:33,940
it's not impossible for us
to work together.

610
00:24:36,920 --> 00:24:38,070
Actually, I've known for a long time

611
00:24:38,070 --> 00:24:39,200
that Xia Ziyu was sent by you

612
00:24:39,200 --> 00:24:40,460
to Chairman Du's side.

613
00:24:40,750 --> 00:24:41,960
Whether you admitted it or not

614
00:24:41,960 --> 00:24:43,490
wouldn't change anything.

615
00:24:43,630 --> 00:24:44,640
Anyway, this bad move

616
00:24:44,640 --> 00:24:46,040
has already been played.

617
00:24:47,030 --> 00:24:47,750
So,

618
00:24:47,920 --> 00:24:50,250
you were just waiting for me
to come clean?

619
00:24:50,920 --> 00:24:52,250
How could I be so stupid?

620
00:24:54,030 --> 00:24:54,760
Don't worry.

621
00:24:55,180 --> 00:24:56,160
Since I had the means

622
00:24:56,160 --> 00:24:57,550
to send her to Old Man,

623
00:24:58,030 --> 00:24:59,920
I have the means
to make her disappear immediately.

624
00:24:59,920 --> 00:25:00,590
Forget it.

625
00:25:01,160 --> 00:25:02,270
You've only just gotten your life

626
00:25:02,270 --> 00:25:03,800
on track in Shengcheng.

627
00:25:04,000 --> 00:25:05,440
Breaking the law for her

628
00:25:06,200 --> 00:25:07,200
won't be worth it.

629
00:25:08,730 --> 00:25:14,530
♪ Love has become a burden,
and being in love feels like a torment ♪

630
00:25:14,950 --> 00:25:20,390
♪ My heart is now filled with
bitter tears ♪

631
00:25:17,750 --> 00:25:19,590
She told me not to break the law.

632
00:25:20,980 --> 00:25:27,220
♪ Old feelings were intoxicating,
now I fear chasing them again ♪

633
00:25:21,680 --> 00:25:22,880
So she cares about me?

634
00:25:26,510 --> 00:25:27,240
Definitely.

635
00:25:27,840 --> 00:25:32,240
♪ Yet my infatuated heart
still longs to see you ♪

636
00:25:28,790 --> 00:25:30,520
She definitely cares about me.

637
00:25:33,160 --> 00:25:33,690
How much?

638
00:25:35,240 --> 00:25:36,240
Six. Six yuan.

639
00:25:36,590 --> 00:25:36,880
Alright.

640
00:25:36,880 --> 00:25:37,680
Here's 6 yuan.

641
00:25:37,690 --> 00:25:38,240
Come again.

642
00:25:38,240 --> 00:25:38,640
Okay.

643
00:25:44,960 --> 00:25:45,510
Junbao,

644
00:25:46,400 --> 00:25:47,350
what are you looking at?

645
00:25:47,350 --> 00:25:48,160
Get to work.

646
00:25:48,510 --> 00:25:49,110
Coming up.

647
00:25:49,130 --> 00:25:49,880
It's busy hour.

648
00:25:49,880 --> 00:25:51,010
Eat while it's warm.

649
00:25:54,440 --> 00:25:54,880
Drive.

650
00:25:55,750 --> 00:25:56,480
To Elegance.

651
00:26:05,780 --> 00:26:09,440
[Grand Opening of Golden Sands Pool]

652
00:26:21,790 --> 00:26:23,650
Why am I hearing that sound again?

653
00:26:40,150 --> 00:26:41,240
My dear Ms. Xia.

654
00:26:41,510 --> 00:26:43,400
You handle everything personally.

655
00:26:43,400 --> 00:26:44,240
Imagine how much pressure

656
00:26:44,240 --> 00:26:45,570
that puts on your staff.

657
00:26:53,680 --> 00:26:54,340
Zhou Cheng.

658
00:26:55,640 --> 00:26:56,720
I don't know why,

659
00:26:57,010 --> 00:26:58,450
but I've been having

660
00:26:58,480 --> 00:26:59,680
a bad feeling lately.

661
00:27:00,400 --> 00:27:01,070
In my mind,

662
00:27:01,070 --> 00:27:02,310
I keep seeing sudden images

663
00:27:02,310 --> 00:27:03,240
of a fire.

664
00:27:04,350 --> 00:27:05,000
It might be a glimpse of

665
00:27:05,000 --> 00:27:06,310
a future I've seen,

666
00:27:07,550 --> 00:27:09,640
but because my memories are all mixed up,

667
00:27:09,640 --> 00:27:11,500
I can't really recall it clearly.

668
00:27:11,960 --> 00:27:13,890
It makes me feel extremely uneasy.

669
00:27:15,510 --> 00:27:16,160
A fire?

670
00:27:19,310 --> 00:27:21,000
Since we can't confirm

671
00:27:21,000 --> 00:27:22,000
what the event is,

672
00:27:22,590 --> 00:27:23,680
let's take precautions

673
00:27:23,680 --> 00:27:24,440
in advance.

674
00:27:25,070 --> 00:27:25,800
For example,

675
00:27:26,310 --> 00:27:27,270
regarding the decor,

676
00:27:27,270 --> 00:27:28,560
reduce flammables,

677
00:27:28,590 --> 00:27:29,720
and ban open flames.

678
00:27:31,200 --> 00:27:31,590
Okay.

679
00:27:33,790 --> 00:27:35,120
Then help me check again

680
00:27:35,270 --> 00:27:36,000
if there's anything else

681
00:27:36,000 --> 00:27:37,460
that needs to be adjusted.

682
00:27:46,830 --> 00:27:49,310
Make sure all the decorations
are properly hung.

683
00:27:49,310 --> 00:27:50,640
And make sure everything looks neat

684
00:27:50,640 --> 00:27:51,570
and harmonious.

685
00:27:52,070 --> 00:27:52,530
Ge Jian.

686
00:27:52,990 --> 00:27:54,360
These are too flammable.

687
00:27:54,360 --> 00:27:54,960
Better forget it.

688
00:27:54,960 --> 00:27:56,090
Just take them down.

689
00:27:56,590 --> 00:27:57,390
Okay, Ms. Xia.

690
00:27:57,400 --> 00:27:57,920
Well,

691
00:27:58,200 --> 00:27:59,240
stop what you're doing.

692
00:27:59,240 --> 00:28:00,070
We're not hanging them up anymore.

693
00:28:00,070 --> 00:28:00,790
Take them down. Take them down.

694
00:28:00,790 --> 00:28:01,520
Okay. Got it.

695
00:28:01,750 --> 00:28:02,130
Come on,

696
00:28:02,130 --> 00:28:02,440
take them down.

697
00:28:02,440 --> 00:28:04,500
Thank you for your hard work.
Come on.

698
00:28:06,270 --> 00:28:06,920
Relax.

699
00:28:07,160 --> 00:28:08,360
Don't worry too much.

700
00:28:09,240 --> 00:28:09,640
Go sit.

701
00:28:09,660 --> 00:28:10,590
I'll get you a glass of water.

702
00:28:10,590 --> 00:28:11,000
Okay.

703
00:28:24,510 --> 00:28:25,590
An explosion occurred on the opening day

704
00:28:25,590 --> 00:28:27,600
of a property development in Shengcheng.

705
00:28:27,600 --> 00:28:29,240
Firefighters rushed to the scene
immediately

706
00:28:29,240 --> 00:28:31,040
to carry out rescue operations.

707
00:28:33,030 --> 00:28:33,440
Here.

708
00:28:34,310 --> 00:28:34,840
Xiaolan.

709
00:28:43,030 --> 00:28:43,830
What's wrong?

710
00:28:44,480 --> 00:28:45,140
Explosion.

711
00:28:46,160 --> 00:28:47,220
It's an explosion.

712
00:28:47,680 --> 00:28:48,720
I remember when I was young,

713
00:28:48,720 --> 00:28:50,160
I saw it on the TV news.

714
00:28:50,590 --> 00:28:52,480
In the 90s, there was a development

715
00:28:52,480 --> 00:28:54,340
that exploded on its opening day.

716
00:28:54,670 --> 00:28:56,400
Many homebuyers were injured.

717
00:28:56,550 --> 00:28:57,160
And later, that development

718
00:28:57,160 --> 00:28:57,880
was never sold—

719
00:28:57,880 --> 00:29:01,010
it became an abandoned,
unfinished building in the end.

720
00:29:02,450 --> 00:29:04,110
Since we already know about it

721
00:29:04,240 --> 00:29:06,060
and have taken protective measures,

722
00:29:06,060 --> 00:29:06,960
let's not worry excessively

723
00:29:06,960 --> 00:29:07,750
about things

724
00:29:07,770 --> 00:29:09,270
that haven't happened yet.

725
00:29:09,270 --> 00:29:09,880
Besides,

726
00:29:10,270 --> 00:29:11,530
the news in your memory

727
00:29:11,680 --> 00:29:13,740
might not be about Golden Sands Pool.

728
00:29:13,830 --> 00:29:15,090
Don't scare yourself.

729
00:29:15,350 --> 00:29:15,830
In a bit,

730
00:29:16,220 --> 00:29:17,830
I'll have all these hydrogen balloons

731
00:29:17,830 --> 00:29:18,750
taken down.

732
00:29:19,750 --> 00:29:20,200
Okay?

733
00:29:22,750 --> 00:29:23,200
Okay.

734
00:29:24,440 --> 00:29:25,170
Don't worry.

735
00:29:28,460 --> 00:29:31,840
[Grand Opening of Golden Sands Pool]

736
00:29:46,680 --> 00:29:47,480
Get me a drink.

737
00:29:48,880 --> 00:29:50,280
Why are you in such a rush?

738
00:29:53,890 --> 00:29:55,750
You used to be a boss in Longcheng,

739
00:29:56,000 --> 00:29:57,270
and now you live like a rat

740
00:29:57,270 --> 00:29:58,510
in this tiny dump

741
00:29:58,510 --> 00:29:59,880
of Shengcheng.

742
00:30:02,640 --> 00:30:04,640
What is it? Speak!

743
00:30:04,920 --> 00:30:05,510
Yixiong.

744
00:30:06,160 --> 00:30:08,560
Golden Sands Pool opens for sale tomorrow.

745
00:30:15,790 --> 00:30:18,200
Every piece of trash has its use.

746
00:30:18,880 --> 00:30:20,280
Make sure tomorrow's job

747
00:30:20,310 --> 00:30:21,240
gets done right.

748
00:30:21,920 --> 00:30:22,720
Do you hear me?

749
00:30:25,550 --> 00:30:26,200
Yixiong.

750
00:30:27,200 --> 00:30:28,030
That rich woman

751
00:30:28,030 --> 00:30:29,090
who came to see you—

752
00:30:29,480 --> 00:30:30,790
will she keep her word?

753
00:30:31,830 --> 00:30:32,400
What?

754
00:30:33,060 --> 00:30:34,590
You spent a few days behind the bars,

755
00:30:34,590 --> 00:30:35,890
and you've lost your nerve?

756
00:30:35,890 --> 00:30:37,240
Too scared to act without help now?

757
00:30:37,240 --> 00:30:38,070
Of course not.

758
00:30:38,790 --> 00:30:40,450
Even without that rich woman,

759
00:30:41,030 --> 00:30:42,640
we'll still avenge Liu.

760
00:30:43,000 --> 00:30:43,800
That's right.

761
00:30:44,240 --> 00:30:44,890
Absolutely. We must.

762
00:30:44,890 --> 00:30:45,570
We must.

763
00:30:53,880 --> 00:30:54,590
Yaozong.

764
00:30:55,410 --> 00:30:57,000
Let's drink to our heart's content today.

765
00:30:57,000 --> 00:30:57,460
Cheers.

766
00:30:57,460 --> 00:30:58,050
So happy.

767
00:30:58,790 --> 00:30:59,790
Have another sip.

768
00:31:01,710 --> 00:31:02,440
That's the spirit.

769
00:31:02,440 --> 00:31:03,070
Yaozong.

770
00:31:05,440 --> 00:31:06,700
I can't drink anymore.

771
00:31:10,550 --> 00:31:11,080
Yaozong?

772
00:31:16,030 --> 00:31:17,720
When you do your rounds tonight,

773
00:31:17,720 --> 00:31:19,310
make sure to check carefully.

774
00:31:19,310 --> 00:31:19,790
Okay.

775
00:31:20,000 --> 00:31:21,250
Check every building.

776
00:31:21,250 --> 00:31:22,510
Make sure there are no hazards.

777
00:31:22,510 --> 00:31:22,920
Okay.

778
00:31:30,470 --> 00:31:31,200
Who's there?

779
00:31:31,590 --> 00:31:32,650
What are you doing?

780
00:31:32,960 --> 00:31:33,830
He's stealing rebars!

781
00:31:33,830 --> 00:31:34,240
Get him!

782
00:31:34,240 --> 00:31:35,030
You guys, get him!

783
00:31:35,030 --> 00:31:35,490
Get him!

784
00:31:35,500 --> 00:31:36,290
Cut him off here!

785
00:31:36,290 --> 00:31:36,890
Catch him!

786
00:31:37,200 --> 00:31:37,860
Cut him off!

787
00:31:38,960 --> 00:31:39,960
Stop right there!

788
00:31:56,550 --> 00:31:57,030
Call the police.

789
00:31:57,030 --> 00:31:58,070
Call an ambulance! Quick!

790
00:31:58,070 --> 00:31:59,000
Yes, Manager Ge.

791
00:32:01,510 --> 00:32:02,240
Luo Yaozong?

792
00:32:03,160 --> 00:32:03,890
Luo Yaozong!

793
00:32:24,960 --> 00:32:25,360
Hello?

794
00:32:26,070 --> 00:32:26,530
Ms. Xia.

795
00:32:26,830 --> 00:32:29,750
Luo Yaozong fell from a building
at the construction site.

796
00:32:29,750 --> 00:32:31,320
Ge Jian, call the police immediately

797
00:32:31,320 --> 00:32:32,110
and secure the scene.

798
00:32:32,110 --> 00:32:33,110
Don't touch anything.

799
00:32:33,110 --> 00:32:34,240
I'll be right there.

800
00:32:39,920 --> 00:32:40,980
Hello? Zhou Cheng.

801
00:32:41,030 --> 00:32:43,560
Something bad happened
at Golden Sands Pool.

802
00:32:51,030 --> 00:32:51,490
Ms. Xia.

803
00:32:52,270 --> 00:32:53,350
How is Luo Yaozong?

804
00:32:53,510 --> 00:32:54,280
He's lucky to be alive.

805
00:32:54,280 --> 00:32:55,280
The place he fell

806
00:32:55,310 --> 00:32:56,680
happened to be where Mr. Wu

807
00:32:56,680 --> 00:32:57,720
had sand piled up.

808
00:32:57,930 --> 00:32:58,680
Was he in cahoots

809
00:32:58,680 --> 00:32:59,740
with the rebar thief?

810
00:32:59,740 --> 00:33:00,550
We don't know yet.

811
00:33:00,550 --> 00:33:01,760
We'll have to wait for
the police to investigate.

812
00:33:01,760 --> 00:33:02,680
Mr. Zhou and Mr. Liu

813
00:33:02,680 --> 00:33:04,310
are waiting for the police
at Golden Sands Pool.

814
00:33:04,310 --> 00:33:06,310
They asked me to bring Luo Yaozong
to the hospital first.

815
00:33:06,310 --> 00:33:06,790
Okay.

816
00:33:08,160 --> 00:33:08,590
San.

817
00:33:09,070 --> 00:33:10,830
I'll leave things here to you and Zhenzhu.

818
00:33:10,830 --> 00:33:12,270
Leave it to us. Don't worry.

819
00:33:12,270 --> 00:33:12,750
Ge Jian,

820
00:33:13,000 --> 00:33:14,000
come back with me.

821
00:33:14,270 --> 00:33:14,930
The trouble

822
00:33:15,400 --> 00:33:16,350
has just begun.

823
00:33:17,110 --> 00:33:17,710
We're off.

824
00:33:17,830 --> 00:33:18,960
Stay safe, you guys.

825
00:33:21,830 --> 00:33:24,030
Here's the security guard duty roster.

826
00:33:24,590 --> 00:33:26,110
The person involved has been taken
to the hospital.

827
00:33:26,110 --> 00:33:27,200
As for the details,

828
00:33:27,480 --> 00:33:28,740
we're not sure either.

829
00:33:35,240 --> 00:33:36,100
This is Ms. Xia.

830
00:33:37,920 --> 00:33:38,480
Xiaolan.

831
00:33:41,590 --> 00:33:42,520
Hello, Officer.

832
00:33:42,830 --> 00:33:43,960
I'm the person in charge of
Golden Sands Pool,

833
00:33:43,960 --> 00:33:44,690
Xia Xiaolan.

834
00:33:45,240 --> 00:33:45,740
Luo Yaozong

835
00:33:45,740 --> 00:33:46,800
is indeed one of our security guards.

836
00:33:46,800 --> 00:33:47,590
But tonight,

837
00:33:47,590 --> 00:33:49,160
we didn't schedule him for a shift.

838
00:33:49,160 --> 00:33:49,880
And Golden Sands Pool

839
00:33:49,880 --> 00:33:51,140
goes on sale tomorrow.

840
00:33:51,270 --> 00:33:53,160
Please make sure to investigate this
thoroughly as soon as possible.

841
00:33:53,160 --> 00:33:54,030
If things get out of hand,

842
00:33:54,030 --> 00:33:55,890
it will be very difficult for us
to manage.

843
00:33:55,890 --> 00:33:56,830
As for Luo Yaozong's situation,

844
00:33:56,830 --> 00:33:58,270
Mr. Zhou has told me about it.

845
00:33:58,270 --> 00:33:59,960
I've also checked the duty roster.

846
00:33:59,960 --> 00:34:00,830
And the others

847
00:34:00,850 --> 00:34:01,880
who were with Luo Yaozong

848
00:34:01,880 --> 00:34:03,590
have been taken to the police station.

849
00:34:03,590 --> 00:34:05,390
This case is indeed suspicious.

850
00:34:05,790 --> 00:34:07,200
We will get to the bottom of it.

851
00:34:07,200 --> 00:34:07,550
Okay.

852
00:34:08,190 --> 00:34:08,989
Officer Wang.

853
00:34:09,630 --> 00:34:10,480
Go with Mr. Liu

854
00:34:10,480 --> 00:34:11,440
to the crime scene again

855
00:34:11,440 --> 00:34:12,550
and see if there are any other clues.

856
00:34:12,550 --> 00:34:12,960
Yes, Sir.

857
00:34:12,960 --> 00:34:13,690
Come with me.

858
00:34:15,760 --> 00:34:16,219
Ms. Xia.

859
00:34:16,320 --> 00:34:17,710
Did you come from the hospital?

860
00:34:17,710 --> 00:34:18,110
Yes.

861
00:34:18,440 --> 00:34:19,840
How is Luo Yaozong doing?

862
00:34:20,510 --> 00:34:22,310
He's still being resuscitated.

863
00:34:22,550 --> 00:34:25,320
A life for a life! A life for a life!

864
00:34:25,320 --> 00:34:26,150
My grandson!

865
00:34:26,150 --> 00:34:34,440
A life for a life! A life for a life!

866
00:34:34,460 --> 00:34:35,980
Give me back my son!

867
00:34:36,440 --> 00:34:38,070
Yaozong was killed by them!

868
00:34:38,110 --> 00:34:39,159
A life for a life!

869
00:34:39,190 --> 00:34:40,550
Pay with your life, do you hear us?

870
00:34:40,550 --> 00:34:42,150
You shameless bitch!

871
00:34:42,719 --> 00:34:43,639
I'll kill you!

872
00:34:43,670 --> 00:34:45,550
A life for a life!

873
00:34:45,550 --> 00:34:46,190
What are you trying to do?

874
00:34:46,190 --> 00:34:46,920
Officers...

875
00:34:47,070 --> 00:34:48,870
They're so powerful and influential.

876
00:34:48,870 --> 00:34:50,000
Did you all see that?

877
00:34:50,570 --> 00:34:51,600
Even the police

878
00:34:51,630 --> 00:34:52,830
are siding with them!

879
00:34:53,110 --> 00:34:53,510
Right!

880
00:34:53,630 --> 00:34:55,630
Capitalists are harming the people!

881
00:34:55,630 --> 00:34:57,110
Even the police are in their pocket!

882
00:34:57,110 --> 00:34:57,440
Yeah!

883
00:34:57,670 --> 00:34:59,110
Let's rush them!

884
00:34:59,360 --> 00:35:00,230
Those two

885
00:35:00,230 --> 00:35:01,250
who were inciting the Luo family just now—

886
00:35:01,250 --> 00:35:02,390
follow them quietly.

887
00:35:02,390 --> 00:35:02,800
Right?

888
00:35:02,880 --> 00:35:04,230
They killed Yaozong!

889
00:35:04,510 --> 00:35:05,190
We have to see him,

890
00:35:05,190 --> 00:35:05,960
alive

891
00:35:06,150 --> 00:35:06,840
or dead!

892
00:35:07,070 --> 00:35:07,590
That's right!

893
00:35:07,590 --> 00:35:08,480
A life for a life!

894
00:35:08,480 --> 00:35:09,440
Stop, stop!

895
00:35:10,110 --> 00:35:10,670
Wait, wait!

896
00:35:10,670 --> 00:35:12,070
Stop making a scene here!

897
00:35:12,710 --> 00:35:14,150
Once we get to the bottom of it,

898
00:35:14,150 --> 00:35:15,410
we won't favor anyone.

899
00:35:15,550 --> 00:35:16,610
Make way, make way!

900
00:35:16,800 --> 00:35:17,930
Excuse me! Make way!

901
00:35:19,030 --> 00:35:20,290
Put down your weapons!

902
00:35:21,710 --> 00:35:22,360
Officers.

903
00:35:22,840 --> 00:35:24,580
We're from the Subdistrict Office.

904
00:35:24,580 --> 00:35:25,310
Luo Degui.

905
00:35:25,760 --> 00:35:27,030
What do you think you're doing?

906
00:35:27,030 --> 00:35:28,760
Do you want to lose your job
as Village Director or what?

907
00:35:28,760 --> 00:35:30,190
My son is dead.

908
00:35:30,710 --> 00:35:32,570
Whoever wants the job can take it.

909
00:35:32,760 --> 00:35:34,370
I don't give a damn!

910
00:35:34,400 --> 00:35:34,670
Yeah!

911
00:35:34,670 --> 00:35:36,000
Give me back my son!

912
00:35:36,610 --> 00:35:37,280
Calm down, everyone!

913
00:35:37,280 --> 00:35:38,710
Officer, let me say something.

914
00:35:38,710 --> 00:35:39,320
Calm down!

915
00:35:39,720 --> 00:35:40,810
Do you want to know

916
00:35:40,840 --> 00:35:42,240
how Luo Yaozong's doing?

917
00:35:42,480 --> 00:35:44,110
If you do, then shut up!

918
00:35:45,880 --> 00:35:47,210
Luo Yaozong isn't dead.

919
00:35:47,960 --> 00:35:48,960
He's still alive.

920
00:35:52,510 --> 00:35:53,940
If you don't want to see him

921
00:35:53,940 --> 00:35:55,320
and just want to cause trouble,

922
00:35:55,320 --> 00:35:56,720
then keep making a scene.

923
00:35:58,320 --> 00:35:59,050
She's lying!

924
00:35:59,550 --> 00:36:01,150
Luo Yaozong is already dead.

925
00:36:01,360 --> 00:36:03,110
Falling from such a high building—

926
00:36:03,110 --> 00:36:04,230
how could he possibly survive?

927
00:36:04,230 --> 00:36:04,630
Right!

928
00:36:04,840 --> 00:36:06,480
How did Yaozong fall?

929
00:36:06,510 --> 00:36:06,880
Exactly!

930
00:36:06,880 --> 00:36:08,280
Did you have someone push him?

931
00:36:08,280 --> 00:36:09,320
Did you push him?

932
00:36:09,440 --> 00:36:10,280
Fell?

933
00:36:11,900 --> 00:36:13,220
How do you know he fell?

934
00:36:15,030 --> 00:36:15,920
I never said

935
00:36:15,920 --> 00:36:17,590
Luo Yaozong fell.

936
00:36:17,760 --> 00:36:18,400
I... I...

937
00:36:19,920 --> 00:36:21,530
I... I heard it from them!

938
00:36:21,960 --> 00:36:22,760
Right, Baldy?

939
00:36:22,870 --> 00:36:23,600
They said it!

940
00:36:23,710 --> 00:36:24,510
Y-Yeah, right!

941
00:36:24,510 --> 00:36:25,550
I... I also heard

942
00:36:25,920 --> 00:36:26,930
i-it from others.

943
00:36:26,960 --> 00:36:28,670
Who exactly did you hear it from?

944
00:36:28,670 --> 00:36:30,030
There must be a source, right?

945
00:36:30,030 --> 00:36:30,510
Yeah.

946
00:36:32,960 --> 00:36:34,620
Fellow villagers of Ganquan.

947
00:36:35,920 --> 00:36:37,280
Luo Yaozong is not dead.

948
00:36:37,920 --> 00:36:40,030
He's undergoing emergency treatment
at the hospital at this moment.

949
00:36:40,030 --> 00:36:41,030
Regarding this matter,

950
00:36:41,030 --> 00:36:42,590
we will investigate thoroughly

951
00:36:42,590 --> 00:36:44,190
and give everyone an answer.

952
00:36:44,440 --> 00:36:45,150
However,

953
00:36:45,960 --> 00:36:47,440
until the truth is out,

954
00:36:47,920 --> 00:36:48,480
if anyone

955
00:36:48,670 --> 00:36:49,920
incites the crowd

956
00:36:49,920 --> 00:36:51,000
to riot again,

957
00:36:51,590 --> 00:36:52,790
we will make arrests.

958
00:36:53,000 --> 00:36:53,660
My grandson

959
00:36:54,030 --> 00:36:55,030
really isn't dead?

960
00:36:55,030 --> 00:36:55,960
H-He's really not dead?

961
00:36:55,960 --> 00:36:56,620
He's alive.

962
00:36:57,320 --> 00:36:58,070
Chief Luo.

963
00:36:58,440 --> 00:37:01,190
Luo Yaozong is being resuscitated
in the hospital right now.

964
00:37:01,190 --> 00:37:03,190
Which is more important—
your grandson's life

965
00:37:03,190 --> 00:37:04,250
or causing a scene?

966
00:37:05,550 --> 00:37:06,190
Someone

967
00:37:06,510 --> 00:37:07,880
must be behind this.

968
00:37:09,040 --> 00:37:09,840
Get the villagers

969
00:37:09,840 --> 00:37:10,770
to go home first.

970
00:37:11,320 --> 00:37:12,150
I promise

971
00:37:12,400 --> 00:37:14,060
I'll get to the bottom of this.

972
00:37:16,190 --> 00:37:17,550
If my grandson dies,

973
00:37:19,440 --> 00:37:20,770
I'll have the villagers

974
00:37:21,510 --> 00:37:23,110
tear down your shabby house.

975
00:37:23,880 --> 00:37:25,030
Then I'll find a rope

976
00:37:25,670 --> 00:37:27,270
and hang myself at this door!

977
00:37:27,280 --> 00:37:28,030
Let's see

978
00:37:28,630 --> 00:37:30,150
who you can sell to then!

979
00:37:30,570 --> 00:37:31,880
Dad, calm down. Calm down.

980
00:37:31,880 --> 00:37:34,540
As long as Yaozong is okay.
That's what matters.

981
00:37:35,880 --> 00:37:36,510
Folks!

982
00:37:36,800 --> 00:37:39,030
Thank you for standing up for Yaozong.

983
00:37:39,550 --> 00:37:40,860
Officials from the Subdistrict Office

984
00:37:40,860 --> 00:37:41,390
are here,

985
00:37:41,510 --> 00:37:42,760
and so are the police.

986
00:37:43,320 --> 00:37:44,580
Please go back for now.

987
00:37:44,630 --> 00:37:46,440
We'll deal with everything
once Yaozong's out of danger.

988
00:37:46,440 --> 00:37:46,920
Go back.

989
00:37:47,230 --> 00:37:48,960
Let's go, folks. Let's go home.

990
00:37:52,550 --> 00:37:52,960
Stop!

991
00:37:53,150 --> 00:37:53,810
Don't move.

992
00:37:53,960 --> 00:37:54,510
What are you doing?

993
00:37:54,510 --> 00:37:55,480
You two can't leave.

994
00:37:55,480 --> 00:37:55,760
Hey,

995
00:37:55,840 --> 00:37:56,670
we are villagers.

996
00:37:56,670 --> 00:37:57,320
Why can't we leave?

997
00:37:57,320 --> 00:37:58,610
Yeah, why can't we go?

998
00:37:58,880 --> 00:37:59,740
Get back there!

999
00:38:00,000 --> 00:38:00,480
Don't move, you hear me?

1000
00:38:00,480 --> 00:38:01,760
I think you two know quite a lot.

1001
00:38:01,760 --> 00:38:02,920
Why don't you explain it to the officers?

1002
00:38:02,920 --> 00:38:03,670
No, this...

1003
00:38:03,710 --> 00:38:04,320
You two,

1004
00:38:04,920 --> 00:38:06,070
come in and have a chat with us.

1005
00:38:06,070 --> 00:38:06,710
Take them away.

1006
00:38:06,710 --> 00:38:08,170
It's none of our business!

1007
00:38:08,950 --> 00:38:10,480
What are you doing? What's this about?

1008
00:38:10,480 --> 00:38:12,210
They have nothing to do with us!

1009
00:38:13,230 --> 00:38:14,160
Leave this to us.

1010
00:38:14,190 --> 00:38:14,590
Okay.

1011
00:38:14,800 --> 00:38:15,690
Thank you then.

1012
00:38:15,920 --> 00:38:17,250
-Let's go.
-Let's go in.

1013
00:38:19,400 --> 00:38:21,000
Yaozong!

1014
00:38:21,510 --> 00:38:22,510
Yaozong!

1015
00:38:22,590 --> 00:38:23,510
Yaozong!

1016
00:38:23,880 --> 00:38:24,670
Yaozong!

1017
00:38:25,480 --> 00:38:26,480
Yaozong!

1018
00:38:26,840 --> 00:38:27,590
Yaozong!

1019
00:38:27,590 --> 00:38:28,190
Calm down. Calm down.

1020
00:38:28,190 --> 00:38:29,240
What are you trying to do?

1021
00:38:29,240 --> 00:38:30,450
My son is in surgery.

1022
00:38:30,480 --> 00:38:31,400
Why won't you let us in?

1023
00:38:31,400 --> 00:38:31,920
Quiet!

1024
00:38:32,110 --> 00:38:33,550
My grandson is in there!

1025
00:38:33,710 --> 00:38:34,770
This is a hospital.

1026
00:38:34,960 --> 00:38:36,160
Family members stay.

1027
00:38:36,190 --> 00:38:37,850
Everyone else, please leave.

1028
00:38:38,920 --> 00:38:39,550
Okay. Okay.

1029
00:38:39,550 --> 00:38:40,080
Officer,

1030
00:38:40,150 --> 00:38:41,150
we'll cooperate.

1031
00:38:41,630 --> 00:38:42,510
You guys go first.

1032
00:38:42,510 --> 00:38:43,570
Go back, everyone.

1033
00:38:44,920 --> 00:38:45,450
Officer.

1034
00:38:45,710 --> 00:38:46,970
I'm Yaozong's father.

1035
00:38:47,000 --> 00:38:48,190
This is Yaozong's grandfather.

1036
00:38:48,190 --> 00:38:49,320
We're both his family.

1037
00:38:49,320 --> 00:38:50,360
Can we go in now?

1038
00:38:50,840 --> 00:38:52,590
Your son is in surgery in there.

1039
00:38:52,840 --> 00:38:53,960
Just wait a moment for now.

1040
00:38:53,960 --> 00:38:54,760
Wait a moment.

1041
00:38:56,280 --> 00:38:57,230
Sit down first.

1042
00:38:58,880 --> 00:39:00,670
I just got off the phone with the station.

1043
00:39:00,670 --> 00:39:01,870
We've confirmed that

1044
00:39:02,150 --> 00:39:03,140
those who were stealing the steel

1045
00:39:03,140 --> 00:39:04,220
with Luo Yaozong

1046
00:39:04,510 --> 00:39:06,170
aren't from Ganquan Village.

1047
00:39:06,440 --> 00:39:07,970
They weren't close before.

1048
00:39:08,510 --> 00:39:10,410
But recently,
they started drinking together

1049
00:39:10,410 --> 00:39:11,760
and got close all of a sudden.

1050
00:39:11,760 --> 00:39:13,560
Clearly, someone planned this.

1051
00:39:14,320 --> 00:39:15,590
We've looked into Luo Yaozong.

1052
00:39:15,590 --> 00:39:16,320
He

1053
00:39:16,320 --> 00:39:17,800
usually throws his weight around,

1054
00:39:17,800 --> 00:39:18,550
but he doesn't really have

1055
00:39:18,550 --> 00:39:20,000
any major grudges with anyone.

1056
00:39:20,000 --> 00:39:20,960
So we suspect...

1057
00:39:21,190 --> 00:39:22,550
Someone's trying to use him

1058
00:39:22,550 --> 00:39:23,710
to cause a fatal accident,

1059
00:39:23,710 --> 00:39:25,370
targeting Golden Sands Pool.

1060
00:39:26,360 --> 00:39:26,820
Ms. Xia,

1061
00:39:27,360 --> 00:39:29,510
have you had any conflicts

1062
00:39:29,760 --> 00:39:31,480
or made any enemies recently?

1063
00:39:32,470 --> 00:39:34,400
No specific conflicts or grudges.

1064
00:39:35,500 --> 00:39:36,250
But I do have

1065
00:39:36,280 --> 00:39:37,340
2 suspects in mind.

1066
00:39:37,800 --> 00:39:38,840
Only those two

1067
00:39:39,080 --> 00:39:39,840
are capable of

1068
00:39:39,840 --> 00:39:41,570
such disregard for human life.

1069
00:39:42,710 --> 00:39:43,880
One is Ke Yixiong,

1070
00:39:44,510 --> 00:39:45,910
and the other is Xia Ziyu.

1071
00:39:47,190 --> 00:39:48,360
We know Ke Yixiong.

1072
00:39:48,800 --> 00:39:49,320
He used to be

1073
00:39:49,320 --> 00:39:50,710
a gang leader

1074
00:39:50,920 --> 00:39:52,070
near Longcheng Railway Station.

1075
00:39:52,070 --> 00:39:53,230
Now that he's in Shengcheng,

1076
00:39:53,230 --> 00:39:54,560
he's still up to no good.

1077
00:39:54,710 --> 00:39:56,030
But he's very cautious.

1078
00:39:56,030 --> 00:39:56,670
When he acts,

1079
00:39:56,670 --> 00:39:57,840
he uses his lackeys,

1080
00:39:58,550 --> 00:39:59,690
keeping himself well-hidden.

1081
00:39:59,690 --> 00:40:01,490
We've been keeping an eye on him.

1082
00:40:01,630 --> 00:40:03,560
A while back, his underling Cao Liu

1083
00:40:03,840 --> 00:40:04,840
hired thugs to attack a friend of mine

1084
00:40:04,840 --> 00:40:05,840
and got locked up.

1085
00:40:06,360 --> 00:40:06,880
There are a few other

1086
00:40:06,880 --> 00:40:08,070
lackeys of his

1087
00:40:08,360 --> 00:40:09,150
who were detained for a few days

1088
00:40:09,150 --> 00:40:10,210
and then released.

1089
00:40:10,400 --> 00:40:11,190
Those are probably the only men

1090
00:40:11,190 --> 00:40:12,230
he has left.

1091
00:40:14,840 --> 00:40:16,240
What about the other one,

1092
00:40:16,280 --> 00:40:16,810
Xia Ziyu?

1093
00:40:16,920 --> 00:40:17,520
Who is she?

1094
00:40:19,070 --> 00:40:20,360
Xia Ziyu is a fugitive.

1095
00:40:21,110 --> 00:40:22,970
She once hired someone to hurt me.

1096
00:40:23,000 --> 00:40:24,730
Later, she fled to Kong Island.

1097
00:40:24,880 --> 00:40:25,590
Officer,

1098
00:40:26,030 --> 00:40:28,510
I suspect the two of them
are conspiring together.

1099
00:40:28,510 --> 00:40:30,170
Can we keep this quiet for now?

1100
00:40:30,440 --> 00:40:31,880
We'll open for sales as planned tomorrow.

1101
00:40:31,880 --> 00:40:33,480
If they have another move planned,

1102
00:40:33,480 --> 00:40:35,010
we can catch them in the act.

1103
00:40:36,840 --> 00:40:38,300
That's all for today then.

1104
00:40:38,320 --> 00:40:39,840
We'll continue the investigation.

1105
00:40:39,840 --> 00:40:40,440
Tomorrow,

1106
00:40:40,510 --> 00:40:42,440
proceed with your sales as normal.

1107
00:40:42,590 --> 00:40:43,840
I'll send plainclothes officers

1108
00:40:43,840 --> 00:40:44,900
to patrol the area.

1109
00:40:45,510 --> 00:40:45,880
Okay.

1110
00:40:46,230 --> 00:40:46,830
Thank you.

1111
00:40:47,960 --> 00:40:48,550
Thank you for your trouble.

1112
00:40:48,550 --> 00:40:49,150
Thank you.

1113
00:40:57,590 --> 00:40:58,790
Let me drive you home.

1114
00:40:58,920 --> 00:41:00,450
So you can have a good sleep.

1115
00:41:00,800 --> 00:41:01,880
Let's not go back and forth.

1116
00:41:01,880 --> 00:41:03,340
I'll just sleep in the car.

1117
00:41:04,760 --> 00:41:05,360
All right.

1118
00:41:21,590 --> 00:41:23,790
I took every precaution against a fire,

1119
00:41:24,710 --> 00:41:27,840
but I never expected the accident
to be someone falling.

1120
00:41:28,760 --> 00:41:30,280
My chaotic memories

1121
00:41:31,110 --> 00:41:32,770
and useless precognition...

1122
00:41:33,920 --> 00:41:34,800
Am I unworthy

1123
00:41:34,800 --> 00:41:36,190
of everyone's trust?

1124
00:41:40,800 --> 00:41:41,550
Zhou Cheng.

1125
00:41:42,510 --> 00:41:44,000
Lately, I've been hearing

1126
00:41:44,000 --> 00:41:45,200
the sound of an alarm.

1127
00:41:46,030 --> 00:41:47,880
Do you think it's a warning?

1128
00:41:55,400 --> 00:41:56,530
Don't overthink it.

1129
00:41:57,230 --> 00:41:59,360
What matters most
is dealing with the present.

1130
00:41:59,360 --> 00:42:00,760
You've done really well.

1131
00:42:01,710 --> 00:42:02,630
We've got all the risk factors

1132
00:42:02,630 --> 00:42:03,590
under control.

1133
00:42:05,840 --> 00:42:06,770
You're too tired

1134
00:42:08,000 --> 00:42:09,000
and too tense.

1135
00:42:11,510 --> 00:42:12,480
You need to rest.

1136
00:42:16,150 --> 00:42:17,440
I truly

1137
00:42:18,070 --> 00:42:18,840
hope Luo Yaozong

1138
00:42:18,840 --> 00:42:19,980
can make it through this critical period

1139
00:42:19,980 --> 00:42:20,910
and wake up soon.

1140
00:42:23,190 --> 00:42:25,390
I hope everything can go well tomorrow,

1141
00:42:25,840 --> 00:42:27,300
and I hope all our hard work

1142
00:42:28,070 --> 00:42:29,230
won't go to waste.

1143
00:42:30,800 --> 00:42:31,530
Don't worry.

1144
00:42:32,920 --> 00:42:33,670
It won't.

1145
00:42:37,360 --> 00:42:37,960
Sleep now.

1146
00:42:48,230 --> 00:42:49,290
Get some good rest.

1147
00:42:52,000 --> 00:42:52,510
Okay.

1148
00:42:59,550 --> 00:43:00,030
Go to sleep.
